## Result Pattern Usage

### Command Handler Example
```csharp
public async Task<Result<Guid>> Handle(CreateRepairRequestCommand request, CancellationToken cancellationToken)
{
    var customerResult = await _customerRepository.GetByIdAsync(request.CustomerId);
    if (customerResult.IsFailure)
        return Result<Guid>.Failure(customerResult.Error);
    
    var repairRequest = RepairRequest.Create(request.Description, customerResult.Value);
    if (repairRequest.IsFailure)
        return Result<Guid>.Failure(repairRequest.Error);
    
    await _repairRequestRepository.AddAsync(repairRequest.Value);
    
    return Result<Guid>.Success(repairRequest.Value.Id);
}
```

### Controller Example
```csharp
public class RepairRequestsController : ApiControllerBase
{
    [HttpPost]
    public async Task<IActionResult> CreateRepairRequest(CreateRepairRequestCommand command)
    {
        var result = await Mediator.Send(command);
        
        return HandleResult(result);
    }
}
```

